  <h2>6. Accuracy and upstream data</h2>
  <p>TaxVett retrieves validation data from third-party government sources (EU VIES, UK HMRC, Australian ABR, Norwegian Brønnøysund Register, Singapore IRAS). We relay their responses as faithfully as possible, but we do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of validation results. A "valid" result reflects the status at the time of the query from the upstream source.</p>
  <p>You should not rely solely on TaxVett results to make binding legal or financial decisions without independent verification.</p>

  <h2>7. Service availability</h2>
